</div>
</div><hr>
<h3 id="3-hugo-设置网站主题">3. Hugo 设置网站主题</h3>
<p>可以从 <a href="https://themes.gohugo.io/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreffer ">Hugo Themes</a> 挑选合适的主题进行应用：</p>
<div class="highlight"><div class="chroma">
